OL,3,CFrom Birmingham to a global empire:
OL,4,CTimeline shows Cadbury's sweet success
OL,6,FFrom a small shop in Birmingham to the
OL,7,Fnation's favourite chocolate brand -
OL,8,Fhere we take a look back at the story
OL,9,Fof Cadbury as it celebrates 200 years.
OL,11,FThe global empire, which cemented
OL,12,Fitself as an icon of and , has been
OL,13,Fdelighting the nation's tastebuds for
OL,14,Ftwo centuries.
OL,16,FFrom its humble beginnings in 1824 to
OL,17,Fbecoming an iconic household name,
OL,18,FCadbury has remained a steadfast
OL,19,Fcompanion in the lives of Britons,
OL,20,Fsynonymous with cherished memories and
OL,21,Ftraditions.
