OL,3,CFrom Birmingham to a global empire:
OL,4,CTimeline shows Cadbury's sweet success
OL,6,F1875: First chocolate Easter egg. It
OL,7,Fwas made with dark chocolate and had a
OL,8,Fsmooth, plain surface. They were
OL,9,Ffilled with sugar-coated chocolate
OL,10,Fdrops known as 'dragees'.
OL,12,F1905: Cadbury Dairy Milk launched.
OL,14,F1915: Milk Tray unveiled - Cadbury
OL,15,Fsays before the launch of the Cadbury
OL,16,FTray, gift chocolates were very
OL,17,Fexpensive, so the company opened up a
OL,18,Fway for more people to afford them.
