OL,3,CFrom Birmingham to a global empire:
OL,4,CTimeline shows Cadbury's sweet success
OL,6,F1920: Creation of the Flake - Cadbury
OL,7,FFlake became famous as the chocolate
OL,8,Fthat comes with 99 ice cream cones.
OL,10,F1971: Creme Egg created.
OL,12,F1983: Launch of the Wispa - it was
OL,13,Flaunched nationally in 1983 after a
OL,14,Ftrial run in the North East of
OL,15,FEngland. However, Cadbury discontinued
OL,16,Fit in 2003. Online petitions and
OL,17,Fcampaigns were set up by Wispa fans -
OL,18,Fwith the firm eventually bringing them
OL,19,Fback in 2008.
